      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARMATREE VIOLET (1) was quickly into stride and burnt early from the middle draw where she gave a sight, finishing second (19.87) and beaten 5.5 lengths over 340m at this track. Goes very well from this draw with five wins and three minor placings from 12 starts. Must come into calculations. TRACEY TARO (2) is progressing well scoring last time out (22.57) at Dubbo and bringing up her 14th career win. Is yet to taste defeat at this course and distance. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. In form and can go on with it. SHORTY (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (25.08) in a NG at this track. Has a good record here including five wins. Shapes as one to consider. IMPERIAL CHOP (4) must be respected at his pet track and distance.",
